### Add game to user library (OWNED)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user-games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1",
  "boardGameId": 2,
  "relationship": "OWNED",
  "source": "kickstarter",
  "acquiredAt": "2026-04-12T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Add game to wishlist
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user-games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1",
  "boardGameId": 3,
  "relationship": "WISHLIST"
}

### Add game played elsewhere
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user-games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1",
  "boardGameId": 4,
  "relationship": "PLAYED_ELSEWHERE",
  "source": "friend's copy"
}

### Get user library
GET http://localhost:3000/api/user-games?userId=1